                <circle cx="48" cy="38" r="3" stroke="rgba(237, 100, 166, 0.4)" stroke-width="1.2"/>
                <path stroke="rgba(237, 100, 166, 0.35)" stroke-width="1.2" d="M36 46h14"/>
            </svg>
            <p class="how-it-works-split__eyebrow">How it works</p>
            <h2 class="how-it-works-split__title">See our steps to success</h2>
            <ol class="how-it-works-split__steps">
                <li class="how-it-works-split__step">
                    <span class="how-it-works-split__num" aria-hidden="true">01</span>
                    <div class="how-it-works-split__step-copy">
                        <h3 class="how-it-works-split__step-title">Expert tutors</h3>
                        <p class="how-it-works-split__step-text">Share your child’s goals and level—we match you with a specialist who fits your schedule and teaching style.</p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li class="how-it-works-split__step">
                    <span class="how-it-works-split__num" aria-hidden="true">02</span>
                    <div class="how-it-works-split__step-copy">
                        <h3 class="how-it-works-split__step-title">Clear plan</h3>
                        <p class="how-it-works-split__step-text">Every session has a purpose: skills to practice, feedback you can act on, and a simple view of what’s next.</p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li class="how-it-works-split__step">
                    <span class="how-it-works-split__num" aria-hidden="true">03</span>
                    <div class="how-it-works-split__step-copy">
                        <h3 class="how-it-works-split__step-title">Confident progress</h3>
                        <p class="how-it-works-split__step-text">Short, engaging lessons build habits—so kids stay motivated and families see real improvement over time.</p>
                    </div>
                </li>
            </ol>
        </div>
        <div class="how-it-works-split__visual">
            <img
                src="{{ asset('img/chldrens.jpg') }}"
                alt="Children learning and playing in a bright, friendly space"
                width="960"
                height="720"
                loading="lazy"
                decoding="async"
                class="how-it-works-split__img"
            />
            <a href="#top" class="how-it-works-split__top" aria-label="Back to top">
                <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 19V5M5 12l7-7 7 7"/></svg>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

